# Dart & Flutter

## Practices
- `const` constructors, `final` variables
- Prefer `StatelessWidget`, use `StatefulWidget` only when needed
- `late` over nullable for required fields
- Named parameters for clarity

## Performance
- Defer heavy ops (DB indexes, recurring expenses)
- Use `FutureBuilder`/`StreamBuilder` appropriately
- Minimize rebuilds with proper keys

## Dependencies
- Drift (DB), Provider (state), fl_chart (charts), intl (formatting)

## Patterns
- `FutureBuilder` for async data
- `Consumer` for Provider state
- `ErrorHandler` for feedback
- `formatCurrency()` for money
